page.title: 09Skipping Games Rhymes
page.content: Bumper car, bumper car, number 48 Whizzing round the corner slamming on the brakes. Along comes a policeman, puts me a jail, All I drank was ginger ale. How many bottles did I drink? lO, 2O, 3O, 4O........ Captain Cook sailed the mighty ocean The Waves got higher and higher and over. Captain Cook lost one eye, Captain Cook lost one arm, Captain Cook lost one leg, Captain Cook fell down dead. Teddy bear, teddy bear touch the ground, Teddy bear, teddy bear, turn around, Teddy bear, teddy bear, climb the stairs, Teddy bear, teddy bear say your prayers, Teddy bear, teddy bear turn off the light, Teddy bear, teddy bear spell goodnight. G.O.O.D.N.I.G.H.T.
